  "title": "Admin Assistant / Admin Executive",
  "description": "<p>We are a Architecture Firm looking for an organized Admin Executive to assist Office Manager manage day-to-day office operations.</p><p><br /><strong>Roles & Responsibilities</strong></p><p>· Assist and support the Office Manager with Administrative & HR duties such as ISO Audit, System Managements, Submissions, Renewals, Insurances.</p><p>· Order and manage office supplies and equipment.</p><p>· Attend to incoming calls, letters, and email inquiries.</p><p>· Work independently and collaborate effectively</p><p>· Able to meet tight deadlines</p><p>· Perform any ad-hoc duties as assigned.<br /></p><p><strong>Requirements</strong><br /><br />· Minimum Diploma</p><p>· A fast learner with good working attitude, responsible, punctual, proactive, and service-oriented.</p><p>· Good Computer skills esp in Microsoft Office and Google Forms etc.</p><p>· Well-organized, detail-oriented, and can manage multiple tasks.</p><p>· At least 2 years of working experience in an Administrative role</p><p>· Able to work independently with minimum supervision</p><p>· Any IT troubleshooting Skills are a plus.</p><p>· Only Singaporean/ PR<br /></p><p></p><p><strong>PLEASE APPLY THROUGH THIS PORTAL OR </strong><u><strong>STRICTLY </strong></u><strong>EMAIL ONLY TO ADMIN@3PECOTECTURE.COM</strong></p><p><strong>Any application received to other email address will not be accepted.</strong></p>",
